OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing through the evening, these
OL,7,Foften heavy, but becoming lighter and
OL,8,Fgradually easing through the second
OL,9,Fpart of the night. Staying breezy,
OL,10,Frather cloudy and mild across the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy at first
OL,14,Fwith isolated showers around, some
OL,15,Fbrighter spells developing at times
OL,16,Flater. The odd spot of light rain
OL,17,Fpossible where the cloud thickens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
