OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with some rain or showers
OL,7,FThursday. Turning drier, brighter and
OL,8,Fwarmer thereafter. Very warm on Friday
OL,9,Fand Saturday, although some thundery
OL,10,Fshowers are possible at times.
